# Usage
#
# repology-package-name=version
#
# https://repology.org/projects/?inrepo=debian_stable
#
# Optional per-package configuration via comment extensions
#
# * source: use a different source name to track the version of this package (for example https://packages.debian.org/buster/make)
# * versioning: defaults to loose (https://docs.renovatebot.com/modules/versioning/#loose-versioning)
#
